# VNC in Jetson Nano is so slow
# to solve this, nomachine is recommend.
# in this guide, i'm going to show on how to install nomachine as follow:

1. See this website for details : https://automaticaddison.com/how-to-set-up-the-nvidia-jetson-nano-developer-kit/
2. See this website to kow which armv8 package for jetson nano : https://kb.nomachine.com/AR02R01074
3. Go to the NoMachine website and download the DEB package for ARMv8: https://www.nomachine.com/download/linux&id=30&s=ARM
4. cd Downloads
5. sudo dpkg -i nomachine_7.4.1_1_arm64.deb
6. sudo shutdown -h now
7. Download nomachine software for client (windows, mac or ubuntu) : https://www.nomachine.com/download
8. Read this for more information : https://www.nomachine.com/getting-started-with-nomachine
